>"},{"pid":"cc308b373aa228517817c6069c09f658f2edddb8","tid":285588,"uid":39800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無論開始時有幾清高, 幾偉大既信念, 只要一涉及錢同權力, 一切都會變質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯啦 熱狗從來冇變質過<br />\n光頭佬一直都係為金錢而戰<br />\n一路走來 始終如一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}